<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en-us" />
<link href="/stylesheets/landing.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" />
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.ico">
<!--[if lt IE 7.]>
<script defer type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/pngfix.js"></script>
<![endif]-->
<title>tourb.us | Find Local, Live Music</title>
</head>

<body onload="document.signup.email.focus();">

<div id="content">
	<div id="logo">
		<a href="/"><img src="/images/logo.gif" title="tourbus"></a>
	</div>
	
<div id="border">

	<div id="msg">
	
	Currently tourb.us is in beta while we gather feedback and stomp bugs.
	Soon we're going to be launching a site to help you find live music.
	
	<p>We're concentrating on aggregating shows for the Boston and San Francisco areas 
	at first, but we also need contributions from you. If you're a show promoter, club owner, 
	musician, or just someone who wants to improve their local music scene
	<a href="maito:info@tourb.us">please get in touch.</a>

	<p>If you're interested, you can follow our 
        progress on our <a href="http://blog.tourb.us">development blog.</a>
		
	<p>If you'd like to be notified when tourbus is ready,
	please add your email below.	
        Have more questions? 
        Email us at <a href="mailto:info@tourb.us">info@tourb.us</a>
	</div>

	<div id="signup">

    <%= start_form_tag( {:controller => "public", :action => "beta_signup"}) %>

	<table width="100%" border="0">
	<tr>
	<td>
	Your email address*:
	</td>
	
	<td align="right">
	<%= text_field_tag('email', nil, :size => 30) %>
	</td>
	
	<tr>
	<td>
		&nbsp;
	</td>
	<td align="right">
		<input type=submit id="submit" value="Submit">
	</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
	<td colspan="2">
	<small>*Don't worry, we'll only use your email to let you know when tourbus is ready</small>
	</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
	</form>
	
	</div>
	
	<div id="msg">
      If you've received an invitation to join the beta, please enter the code below. And
      thanks for helping us get the site ready!
	</div>
	<div id="signup">
	 <% if flash[:error] %>
      <div class="error">
        <center><%= img_label_table "exclamation.png", flash[:error] %></center>
      </div>
      <% end %>
      
      <%= start_form_tag( {:controller => "public", :action => "beta"}) %>

	<table width="100%" border="0">
	<tr>
	<td>
	Invitation code:
	</td>
	
	<td align="right">
	 <%= text_field_tag('code', nil, :size => 30) %>
	</td>
	
	<tr>
	<td>
		&nbsp;
	</td>
	<td align="right">
	   <input type=submit id="submit-invite" value="Submit">
	</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
	<%= end_form_tag %>    
	</div>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>